<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Mar1928"><font color="red">28 March 1928</font> <i>Letters III</i> (to Harriet Weaver): We left Dieppe last evening &hellip; I fatigued myself to exhaustion point over <font face="wake">D</font>a. I am glad you like the fable &hellip; I have been reading about the author of &lsquo;Alice&rsquo;. A few things about him are rather curious. He was born a few miles from Warrington and he had a strong stutter and when he wrote he inverted his name like Tristan and Swift &hellip; We return to Paris in a day or two </div>
